死者作致命一擊，沒有意圖亦不想導致任何人死亡，他們承認誤殺罪也顯示一定程度悔意，而第二被告是在酒精影響下犯事，是一時衝動。<br />\n<br />\n法官聽畢陪審團裁決及兩名被告求情後表示，兩名被告參與了一宗兇殘的謀殺案，只因死者對被告及其他的涉事者不尊重就殺死他，是不需要的，而法官對謀殺案並無酌情決定權，只能判處兩名被告終身監禁。<br />\n<br />\n死者的家屬亦有到庭聽審，法官最後向他們作深切慰問，希望結案後他們對事件有個了結，可以好好生活下去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200310/s00001/1583844448439/2008%E5%B9%B4%E5%A4%A9%E7%91%9E%E9%82%A8%E9%BA%A5%E7%95%B6%E5%8B%9E%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BD%E5%9C%8D%E6%AF%86%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%BB-%E5%85%A9%E7%94%B7%E8%AC%80%E6%AE%BA%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E5%88%A4%E7%B5%82%E8%BA%AB%E7%9B%A3%E7%A6%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200310%2Fs00001%2F1583844448439%2F2008%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%2591%259E%25E9%2582%25A8%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%258B%259E%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E5%259C%258D%25E6%25AF%2586%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%2587%25B4%25E6%25AD%25BB-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25AC%2580%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%25B5%2582%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E7%259B%25A3%25E7%25A6%2581&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0sti%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=5da369f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200310%2Fs00001%2F1583844448439%2F2008%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%2591%259E%25E9%2582%25A8%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%258B%259E%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E5%259C%258D%25E6%25AF%2586%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%2587%25B4%25E6%25AD%25BB-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25AC%2580%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%25B5%2582%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E7%259B%25A3%25E7%25A6%2581&h=e288378a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200310/s00001/1583844448439/2008%E5%B9%B4%E5%A4%A9%E7%91%9E%E9%82%A8%E9%BA%A5%E7%95%B6%E5%8B%9E%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BD%E5%9C%8D%E6%